lliblightmodbus (1.40-1) trusty; urgency=low

  * CMake is to replace original messy build system
  * Add user defined function parsing for master and slave
  * Add option to disable master data buffer (pointer to frame returned)
  * Add option to enable invasive master response frame parsing
  * Add register/coil callback functions for slave
  * ModbusSlave now stores last exception built by modbusBuildException
  * Macro defined types replaced with enums
  * Macro function wrappers replaced with static inline functions
  * Improvements in endianness handling
  * Improvements in error handling system
  * New LaTeX documentation

 -- Jacek Wieczorek <mrjjot@gmail.com>  Sun, 1 Jul 2018 19:57:00 +0200


